{"title":"网络渗透测试（一）","uid":"316965cdb9454725a9b8a1bea24a39dc","slug":"网络渗透测试（一）","date":"2022-10-05T06:34:00.000Z","updated":"2022-10-08T08:43:41.522Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/网络渗透测试（一）.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/49fd81141562a77952857718c6ff28f8027ce1.png","content":"<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E7%BB%98%E5%9B%BE.png\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"VMware虚拟机三种网络模式\"><a href=\"#VMware虚拟机三种网络模式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"VMware虚拟机三种网络模式\"></a>VMware虚拟机三种网络模式</h1><h2 id=\"桥接模式\"><a href=\"#桥接模式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"桥接模式\"></a>桥接模式</h2><p>桥接模式就是将主机网卡与虚拟的网卡利用虚拟网桥进行通信。类似于把物理主机虚拟为一个交换机，虚拟机与物理主机一同连接到这个交换机上，在桥接模式下，虚拟机IP地址需要与主机在<strong>同一网段</strong>，如果需要联网，则网关与DNS需要与主机网卡一致。<strong>桥接模式下的虚拟机与物理机在同一网段中，共用一个路由器</strong></p>\n<p>这里可以将虚拟机与主机看作平等的关系，但在同一网端下只有254（1～254）个主机地址，因此在桥接模式下开的虚拟机台数与物理主机台数之和不能超过254个。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E7%BB%98%E5%9B%BE-166521711002829.png\" alt=\"桥接模式\"></p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">桥接模式在设置时可能需要自己去设置一下桥接的网卡，自动选项有时候不管用。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/image-20221008160843842.png\" alt=\"image-20221008160843842\"></p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"NAT模式\"><a href=\"#NAT模式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"NAT模式\"></a>NAT模式</h2><p>在桥接模式中，对于虚拟机的台数有一定限制。而NAT模式就可以解决交接模式台数不够的问题。</p>\n<p>在NAT模式中，主机网卡直接与虚拟NAT设备相连，然后虚拟NAT设备与虚拟DHCP服务器一起连接在虚拟交换机上，这样就实现了虚拟机联网。VMware Network Adapter VMnet8网卡（虚拟机网卡）是为了实现主机与虚拟机之间的通信。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/image-20221007205222943.png\" alt=\"image-20221007205222943\"></p>\n<p>这里可以将主机看作虚拟机的路由器，通过虚拟网卡给虚拟机分配IP，因此主机与虚拟机不在同一网段下。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E7%BB%98%E5%9B%BE-166514898183023.png\" alt=\"NAT模式\"></p>\n<p>这里要注意的是虚拟网卡是用于主机与虚拟机的通讯，虚拟机访问外网时是通过虚拟NAT设备的。我们可以做一个小实践来证明一下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E7%BB%98%E5%9B%BE-166514807186113.png\"></p>\n<p>这里主机ip为<code>192.168.10.34</code>，虚拟机ip为<code>192.168.16.146</code>，在正常情况下他们两个是互相ping的通的：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E7%BB%98%E5%9B%BE-166514830871215.png\"></p>\n<p>如果我们把虚拟网卡禁用了，这个时候就主机就ping不通虚拟机了，但虚拟机依然可以访问外网。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E7%BB%98%E5%9B%BE-166514885150819.png\"></p>\n<p>因此虚拟网卡起到的作用是连接主机到虚拟机，虚拟机访问网络是通过虚拟NAT设备而<strong>不是虚拟网卡</strong>，就像描述的那样是<strong>与主机共享同一IP访问网络。</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E7%BB%98%E5%9B%BE-166514927425725.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"仅主机模式\"><a href=\"#仅主机模式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"仅主机模式\"></a>仅主机模式</h2><p>理解了桥接模式，再来看仅主机模式就简单多了。直接去掉了虚拟NAT设备，不再与外界联通，通过虚拟网卡实现与虚拟机的交互，将虚拟机与外网隔开，仅与主机交互。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E7%BB%98%E5%9B%BE-166521794216631.png\" alt=\"仅主机模式\"></p>\n<p>在这种情况下虚拟机肯定ping不通外网。<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/image-20221008163401744.png\" alt=\"image-20221008163401744\"></p>\n<p>虚拟机间相互可以ping通。<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/image-20221008163523608.png\" alt=\"image-20221008163523608\"></p>\n<p>主机ping的通虚拟机，但虚拟机ping不通主机（可能是因为仅主机模式没有虚拟NAT设备，而虚拟网卡只负责主机到虚拟机的通讯）<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/%E6%9C%AA%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E7%BB%98%E5%9B%BE-166521833971033.png\"></p>\n","feature":true,"text":" VMware虚拟机三种网络模式桥接模式桥接模式就是将主机网卡与虚拟的网卡利用虚拟网桥进行通信。类似于把物理主机虚拟为一个交换机，虚拟机与物理主机一同连接到这个交换机上，在桥接模式下，虚拟机IP地址需要与主机在同一网段，如果需要联网，则网关与DNS需要与主机网卡一致。桥接模式下的...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":940,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"姚总の网络渗透测试课","slug":"姚总の网络渗透测试课","count":1,"path":"api/categories/姚总の网络渗透测试课.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"渗透","slug":"渗透","count":1,"path":"api/tags/渗透.json"},{"name":"课程","slug":"课程","count":1,"path":"api/tags/课程.json"},{"name":"笔记","slug":"笔记","count":1,"path":"api/tags/笔记.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#VMware%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%89%E7%A7%8D%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">VMware虚拟机三种网络模式</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A1%A5%E6%8E%A5%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">桥接模式</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#NAT%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">NAT模式</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%85%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%BA%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">仅主机模式</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"ta0tie","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/2611658-20220705115610884-738130531.png","link":"/","description":"ฅ^•ﻌ•^ฅ","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/ta0tie","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"重合指数与拟重合指数","uid":"daa35ea37f81004878153ffb51fa5a8a","slug":"重合指数","date":"2022-08-19T10:50:00.000Z","updated":"2022-08-21T15:15:43.500Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/重合指数.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/building-g1203094a4_1920.jpg","text":"写这篇博客来潜潜记录一下自己对重合指数的学习。 多表代换密码比较常见的多表代换密码，如维吉尼亚密码，Porta密码等等。他们特征是有一个固定的代换表，由一段固定长度的密钥结合代换表加密明文。 他们的本质其实还是单表代换密码，因为密钥长度有限，相隔一定长度的明文所使用的加密密钥是一...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"24k","symbolsTime":"21 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"CTF-Crypto","slug":"CTF-Crypto","count":1,"path":"api/categories/CTF-Crypto.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Crypto","slug":"Crypto","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Crypto.json"},{"name":"CTF","slug":"CTF","count":1,"path":"api/tags/CTF.json"},{"name":"重合指数","slug":"重合指数","count":1,"path":"api/tags/重合指数.json"},{"name":"维吉尼亚","slug":"维吉尼亚","count":1,"path":"api/tags/维吉尼亚.json"}],"author":{"name":"ta0tie","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ta0tie/blog-img/main/2611658-20220705115610884-738130531.png","link":"/","description":"ฅ^•ﻌ•^ฅ","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/ta0tie","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true}}